==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: When a person meets with a happy occasion, his spirit is cheerful.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén féng xǐshì jīngshén shuǎng

===Proverb===
'''[[人]][[逢]][[喜事]][[精神]][[爽]]'''

# Joy puts heart into a man.

